\s Bwana Yesu Alikuja
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Bwana Yesu \bd*\bd Alikuja \bd*\bd kutafuta wapotevu\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Kwa rehema yake \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  tunapata kuokoka.\bd*
